data.description: Nice 3 bedroom 1 bath brick home sitting on approximately 0.23 acre corner lot in Union City, TN.  This home features a 1 car carport PLUS a detached brick garage.  Approximately 1306 heated square feet with original hardwood floors in most of the home.  Open kitchen and living room, great sized bedrooms and bath.  All of this priced under $150,000!! Call today to view this home before it's sold!
